The thing is, the red ants thinks the black ants are the enemy and vice versa when in reality the real enemy is the person who shook the jar. This is exactly what's happening in society today: Liberal vs Conservative Black vs White Pro Mask vs Anti Mask The real question we need to be asking ourselves is who's shaking the jar and why?
